PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773180726
OL,3,CLawyers march on parliament in protest
OL,4,Cof jury trials plan
OL,6,FITV News has previously reported on
OL,7,Fhow years of delays have seen a
OL,8,Fgrowing number of victims with little
OL,9,Fchoice but to give up on seeking
OL,10,Fjustice, with the current backlog
OL,11,Fresulting in some hearings being
OL,12,Flisted as far ahead as 2030.
OL,14,FBut critics, who include some
OL,15,Fbackbench Labour MPs, fear watering
OL,16,Fdown the right to a jury trial will
OL,17,Fnot tackle the issues at the heart of
OL,18,Fthe criminal justice system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
