FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773180726
OL,3,CLawyers march on parliament in protest
OL,4,Cof jury trials plan
OL,6,FIt has been reported that over 60
OL,7,FLabour MPs are against their
OL,8,Fgovernment's proposals - though it is
OL,9,Fexpected they will abstain, rather
OL,10,Fthan vote against the reforms in the
OL,11,Fvote this afternoon.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FIt is thought that abstaining at this
OL,19,Fstage is part of a strategy to force
OL,20,Fchanges to the bill further down the
OL,21,Fline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
