FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773180726
OL,3,CLawyers march on parliament in protest
OL,4,Cof jury trials plan
OL,6,FKarl Turner, the Labour MP who is
OL,7,Fwidely reported to be leading a
OL,8,Frebellion against the plans,
OL,9,Fpreviously called on his government to
OL,10,F"get a grip on what is really
OL,11,Fhappening in the system".
OL,13,FHe argued that it was a "dereliction
OL,14,Fof duty" to make changes to jury
OL,15,Ftrials without funding more crown
OL,16,Fcourt hearings.
OL,26,@uD@YOUvD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
