PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773180726
OL,3,CLawyers march on parliament in protest
OL,4,Cof jury trials plan
OL,6,FLabour veteran Diane Abbott has also
OL,7,Fpreviously warned against the changes,
OL,8,Fraising concerns that women could
OL,9,F"undoubtedly suffer miscarriages of
OL,10,Fjustice if the right to trial by jury
OL,11,Fis curtailed".
